snippet.title: GingerSnap DEMO NOW AVAILABLE
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD HERE:
https://meepalasheep.itch.io/gingersnap-demo

A 3D Double feature platformer inspired by old school favorites! Collect and combine ingredients for unique abilities!

(Inspirations would include: Sonic, Zelda, Kirby, Mario and Mega Man! )

I will be putting a demo on steam sometime soon, as well. But I would like to polish it a bit, before then.

Also on the offchance people are interested, I've hit some hard times(lost my job) so I'm opening up a patreon! Members get early access to the full game! https://www.patreon.com/Meepalasheep
